{"tid":1623830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共產黨玩嘢，香港人領嘢。咁都領嘢？枉為香港人。","createTime":"2019-10-05T01:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T02:31:26.000Z","uid":78635,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"598e6b996172b833ef648a0f059686ca1454b893","tid":1623830,"uid":78635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:52:45.000Z","msg":"陳雲：<br />\n共產黨玩嘢，香港人領嘢。咁都領嘢？枉為香港人。香港人不聽陳雲的話，犯上政治錯誤，犧牲幾多人都是被共產黨收割，之後糟蹋。<br />\n<br />\n如果你識字，就知道第一句是共產黨的意識形態。破舊立新，而且強調歷史發展的必然性。<br />\n<br />\n香港人昨晚十八區，宣讀共產主義宣言，而且宣言隻字不提美國為香港人權立法監護香港的貢獻，美國的有識之士被香港人激死了。"},{"pid":"4af87d73684c6a51997e7ad496abd44466958fc4","tid":1623830,"uid":78635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:55:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b154d3d4beb62be2644c82133c6ebaf7ef7cdd5","tid":1623830,"uid":78635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:01:17.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"7bb84d3f6b9e578610e87b8ca9d9ae4c3d4a4349","tid":1623830,"uid":78635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:03:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41949d2be308a67c284fc91ee490a5876a9fdbf4","tid":1623830,"uid":78635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:14:48.000Z","msg":"無執政既意志<br />\n無執政既人材<br />\n事前毫無討論<br />\n一時情緒上腦<br />\n成立咩嘢臨政？"},{"pid":"45b6ad992124d98a45901a2e265534034dc4a5ed","tid":1623830,"uid":78635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:15:34.000Z","msg":"咁樣玩膠<br />\n過去四個月的努力有可能前功盡廢的"},{"pid":"a18a621fe16d3749d1f6838471ec5542be8f52b7","tid":1623830,"uid":298833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:28:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3774add7ed9f0314cada303f18dcee5a73cf85b","tid":1623830,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41949d2be308a67c284fc91ee490a5876a9fdbf4","tid":1623830,"uid":78635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T02:14:48.000Z","msg":"無執政既意志<br />\n無執政既人材<br />\n事前毫無討論<